						               													<description>The best alchemists around the globe have reunited to brew the perfect potion!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Add the Magic Scroll' expansion to your copy of The Potion to play the new co-operative mode. Try to match the recipes on the dice in order to get rid of your ingredients. If you fail doing so, you will ruin the potion and have to start again!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players cannot speak. They must use their deduction skills to choose the right ingredients to match what the potion requires to be brewed. Each time a player fails matching the recipe, they put their ingredient beside the bottle. Each time they succeed, they place it inside the bottle.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Win the game by having one alchemist within the group left with only one type of ingredient in hand. However, the more ingredients you put in the bottle, the better the potion you will create...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
